msgstr "Parameter"

#: ipres.election.Election:10 of
msgid ""
"Global configuration for this election (constituencies, parties, majority"
" threshold, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Globale Konfiguration für diese Wahl (Wahlkreise, Parteien, "
"Mehrheitsschwelle usw.)."

#: ipres.election.Election of
msgid "type"
msgstr ""

